159
00:08:39,358 --> 00:08:40,823
Never owe anyone if it's possible.

160
00:08:40,823 --> 00:08:42,660
Otherwise, it'll weigh on you
for the rest of your life.

161
00:08:43,384 --> 00:08:45,891
