that pairs perfectly with this dish.

200
00:12:40,115 --> 00:12:42,217
Okay, let's go with this one.

201
00:12:42,782 --> 00:12:44,124
It has a full body.

202
00:12:44,124 --> 00:12:45,607
It should go well with the steak.

203
00:12:48,150 --> 00:12:50,092
- Thank you.
- Sure, sir.

204
00:12:53,871 --> 00:12:56,238
You seem quite the expert.

205
00:12:56,962 --> 00:12:58,392
I have to know a thing or two,

206
00:12:58,498 --> 00:13:00,140
so I can take good care of my clients.

207
00:13:09,164 --> 00:13:10,647
Thank you.

208
00:13:28,602 --> 00:13:29,882
