222
00:14:12,293 --> 00:14:13,582
How did you end up becoming a host?

223
00:14:17,044 --> 00:14:18,598
My life is like a drama series.

224
00:14:19,745 --> 00:14:20,893
Do you ever watch them, Officer?

225
00:14:22,324 --> 00:14:23,719
(Before this,)

226
00:14:23,736 --> 00:14:26,244
(I used to live the life of
a typical Architecture student.)

227
00:14:26,438 --> 00:14:28,169
(I was so happy when I got accepted,)

228
00:14:28,169 --> 00:14:30,288
(and I truly loved what I was studying.)

229
00:14:32,513 --> 00:14:35,409
(Loan agreement)
Your mom owes us 800,000 baht.

230
00:14:36,274 --> 00:14:37,704
800,000 baht?

231
00:14:37,704 --> 00:14:40,900
(My mom's 800,000 baht debt
hit me like a freight train.)

232
00:14:41,730 --> 00:14:44,309
(It was enough to make me realize
I had to drop out of school.)

233
00:14:44,750 --> 00:14:46,957
(After that, I became 'famous'
at the university.)

234
00:14:47,381 --> 00:14:49,306
(Everyone assumed
I was a gambling addict.)

235
00:14:50,106 --> 00:14:51,390
So what?

236
00:14:51,390 --> 00:14:52,361
