944
00:55:04,882 --> 00:55:05,600
Hey!

945
00:55:06,579 --> 00:55:08,150
Are you for real?

946
00:55:11,594 --> 00:55:13,448
I see something in you.

947
00:55:14,119 --> 00:55:16,273
I think you can help me.

948
00:55:23,248 --> 00:55:25,562
I'm currently investigating
a human trafficking case,

949
00:55:29,923 --> 00:55:31,777
and Chainphop is a person of interest.

950
00:55:38,717 --> 00:55:41,242
We have a lot of CCTV footage.

951
00:55:42,037 --> 00:55:43,785
From what we've gathered,

952
00:55:43,891 --> 00:55:47,634
everyone involved with Chainphop
has gone missing.

953
00:55:52,362 --> 00:55:53,050
Whoa!

954
00:55:55,368 --> 00:55:56,463
That's terrifying.

955
00:55:57,276 --> 00:55:58,777
Yes, it is.

956
00:55:59,872 --> 00:56:00,914
And it won't be easy.

957
00:56:01,585 --> 00:56:03,581
You have every right to refuse.

958
00:56:04,887 --> 00:56:07,042
But if you choose to help me,

959
00:56:07,165 --> 00:56:09,355
I'll assist you financially.

960
00:56:10,008 --> 00:56:12,004
So you can go back to being a student,

961
00:56:12,004 --> 00:56:13,469
